Class DatalogProgram

java.lang.Object

java.lang.Runnable
public class DatalogProgram
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

Converts Tokens created by a Tokenizer into Datalog structures. This can be run as a separate Thread to optimize for speed.
